  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To use this collaborative technique, you must have summoned a Toad with the Spit Oil ability, and said summon must be within 5 ft. of you, both of you ready to act on the same initiative. The toad spits out a long cone of oil, which you ignite with your Chakra to create a blazing cone of destruction. Any creature in the area suffers 8d8 fire damage. If the Toad is Gargantuan, this technique deals 8d10 damage instead, and a Colossal one increases it further to 8d12.<br><br>The cone's length is based on the Toad's size: Medium (30 ft.), Large (50 ft.), Huge (80 ft.), Gargantuan (100 ft.) or Colossal (120 ft.).</p>\n\n\n\n",
